title: Merged changes from Photo Voyages of Trey Ratclif version 1.2
message:
Merged changes from Photo Voyages of Trey Ratclif version 1.2

Save Wallpapers or save the photos for your contacts.
Tap photo to show/hide description
Fixed many memory problems
Smarter use of caching
Last-In/First-out queue for all file IO read events which also ensures
the photo is still in use before it is loaded
Devices with low resolution will get down-sampled photos to match their
resolution (typically using a quarter of the memory for each photo)
Great for Google TV: Pause and Resume menu item!
